---
title: Cheesy Pork & Bean Enchiladas with Sour Cream & Zingy Tomato
description: With beans, tortillas, Cheddar cheese and spiced pork, this Mexican favourite is colourful, delicious and a heap of fun to make. Don’t forget to dollop on the classic sour cream to really get the fiesta going!
